&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt; One damaged, rewritable Blu-Ray disc in the collection of Dr. J. Bright, Director of Foundation Personnel, containing [DATA EXPUNGED].&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Notes:&lt;/strong&gt; Dr. Bright expressed satisfaction at the return of his files, remarking &amp;quot;I thought I&#039;d lost these forever!&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
