&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;border: 1px solid black; padding-right: 12px; padding-top: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 24px;background-color: #F3F3F3&quot; colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Using it as a death signal. Clever. What happened to the fourth agent?&lt;/em&gt; [Blank, Dr. H.]&lt;/td&gt;
