&lt;div class=&quot;scp-image-caption&quot; style=&quot;width:230px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An instance of SCP-5977 in the Toronto Transit Commission (TTC) subway, Ontario, Canada.&lt;/p&gt;
