&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Special Containment Procedures:&lt;/strong&gt; SCP-5056 is contained by the Janitorial and Maintenance Section of &lt;a href=&quot;http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/secure-facility-dossier-site-43&quot;&gt;Site-43&lt;/a&gt;. Its position depends upon, is determined by, and may be directed via the work schedule of Philip Eugene Deering (JM64/SCP-5056-B).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SCP-5056-B is confined to Site-43. He must not be assigned tasks in the research or experimentation laboratories, operating theatres, administrative offices, containment facilities or wetworks of Site-43. He must nevertheless be assigned a daily duty schedule. He is not to be apprised of his SCP status.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SCP-5056-A and B are not to be separated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the event of SCP-5056-B&#039;s death, selected staff will execute SARGENT Protocol to neutralize SCP-5056-A. SARGENT Protocol documents have been forwarded to suitable personnel; personnel who have not received said documents have no additional containment duties in relation to these subjects.&lt;/p&gt;
