				<title>&amp; the Endings Thereof</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/and-the-endings-thereof</link>
				<description>


&lt;p&gt;by &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610249242&quot; alt=&quot;DarkStuff&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff&quot;  &gt;DarkStuff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
